title: Microsoft Stream: Stream tile in Microsoft 365 app launcher enabled for GCC-H and DOD
description:
,Stream tile in Microsoft 365 app launcher will be enabled for GCC-H and DOD and users will be able to use the Stream tile to go to the Stream Start Page on office.com. The Stream tile will be visible for GCC-H and DOD tenants having the SharePoint service plan enabled.
GA date: October CY2022
Preview date: November CY2022
